WEBVTT

00:04.212 --> 00:06.548
(UPBEAT MUSIC PLAYING)

00:22.147 --> 00:25.567
-(SIRENS WAILING)
-(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

00:26.401 --> 00:28.111
DOA's Rita Kendall.

00:28.445 --> 00:31.740
-That's her sister. Found her.
-The one having the animated chat?

00:31.990 --> 00:33.283
OFFICER: Rose Kaplan.

00:34.659 --> 00:39.164
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

00:53.678 --> 00:54.971
DANNY: Didn't take a beating.

00:55.180 --> 00:58.308
She puked herself behind the gag.
Choked to death.

00:59.476 --> 01:00.685
That'd be the worst.

01:02.395 --> 01:06.232
-Can the sister help with what's missing?
-Jewels and a gold coin collection.

01:09.778 --> 01:12.739
(CLEARS THROAT)
I'm Detective Sorenson, Mrs. Kaplan.

01:13.281 --> 01:14.866
I'm very sorry, you losing your sister.

01:15.617 --> 01:19.412
All my health difficulties,
who'd believe she'd go first?

01:19.621 --> 01:22.999
-Any idea who might have done this?
-ROSE: Thief or burglar.

01:23.416 --> 01:25.585
Her... her jewelry and coins are gone.

01:26.377 --> 01:29.089
Would your sister be seen outside
with that jewelry on?

01:29.172 --> 01:32.092
It was divided from our mother.
She never wore it at all.

01:32.342 --> 01:33.927
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

01:34.094 --> 01:37.055
(CLEARS THROAT)
Uh, had she had the coins out lately

01:37.138 --> 01:38.807
to take them in to get appraised
or the like?

01:39.766 --> 01:40.892
I don't know.

01:41.101 --> 01:43.978
Uh, she got irritated
every time I asked about the coins,

01:44.062 --> 01:46.481
-so I stopped asking.
-Was there contention over them coins

01:46.606 --> 01:47.607
between the two of you?

01:47.857 --> 01:52.695
Only that she got the entire collection,
and I got six-person dinner service.

01:53.279 --> 01:57.575
But then, I wasn't the object
of a lifelong crush by Seymour Epstein,

01:57.700 --> 01:59.702
the executor of our mother's will.

02:00.078 --> 02:01.579
Could I see what you're clutching there?

02:05.041 --> 02:07.877
My nephew, Justin, a few years ago.

02:08.378 --> 02:11.881
-He dresses now in darker clothes.
-Did he live with your sister?

02:12.215 --> 02:15.635
No. He lives somewhere
in the East Village.

02:16.094 --> 02:19.013
Involved in some rave-type underground.

02:19.681 --> 02:21.516
DANNY: What does that mean
exactly, Mrs. Kaplan?

02:22.016 --> 02:26.938
He asked me to back him financially
to organize rave-type underground parties,

02:27.021 --> 02:28.648
after Rita turned him down.

02:29.232 --> 02:32.152
He took me to the darkest,
dungeon-like atmosphere of a bar

02:32.235 --> 02:33.778
that I could ever imagine.

02:34.279 --> 02:37.407
This was where Justin wanted to organize
these rave-type parties?

02:37.699 --> 02:41.035
-On a sublet rental basis.
-What was the name of that place?

02:41.327 --> 02:44.038
I asked him why did he
expect me to back him

02:44.122 --> 02:45.290
when his mother wouldn't?

02:45.373 --> 02:49.377
-Do you recall that bar's name?
-The Velvet.

02:49.836 --> 02:51.963
I told him they should
call it the Dungeon.

02:52.172 --> 02:54.632
Fine. We'll suggest that
when we stop there.

02:55.341 --> 02:57.218
If you think of anything else,
Mrs. Kaplan,

02:57.302 --> 03:00.805
or Justin tries to get in touch with you,
would you please make sure you call us?

03:03.099 --> 03:05.310
Got a neighbor saw a suspicious man
in the building.

03:07.478 --> 03:10.148
I'd be more interested if he saw
that battle-ax sneaking out

03:10.356 --> 03:11.816
with a coin collection under her arm.

03:16.404 --> 03:18.281
Mr. Fickman. He just walked up.

03:18.823 --> 03:21.993
Six p.m., yesterday, there was a big,
tall guy in the hall.

03:22.202 --> 03:23.244
I never seen him before.

03:23.369 --> 03:25.121
He said he was making
a prescription delivery.

03:25.371 --> 03:27.165
When I asked which pharmacy,
he ignored me.

03:27.415 --> 03:29.500
What'd the guy look like,
besides being big and tall?

03:29.626 --> 03:31.794
I was headed for work.
I work at Chock Full O' Nuts,

03:31.878 --> 03:33.379
-so I didn't pursue it.
-We understand.

03:33.588 --> 03:35.340
Let's get back to what he looked like.

03:35.715 --> 03:37.550
Seeing this now,
I'm wondering if it's connected.

03:37.675 --> 03:39.844
Hey, describe him immediately.

03:40.053 --> 03:45.767
He was big, uh, tall.
Uh, white, 30-ish, I'd say,

03:45.934 --> 03:49.812
-uh, tattooed, like her ghouly son.
-Whose ghouly son?

03:50.104 --> 03:53.441
-Are you here investigating a murder?
-What, are you gonna be sarcastic now?

03:53.733 --> 03:55.818
The dead woman's son, Mrs. Candell.

03:56.152 --> 04:00.073
Her ghouly son, Justin, is who this guy
was tattooed like, only bigger and taller.

04:00.406 --> 04:04.160
Bigger, taller how'd you like
to be shorter, flat on your face?

04:04.452 --> 04:06.579
Can we stay in touch
with you, Mr. Fickman?

04:06.871 --> 04:08.373
Yeah, you can.

04:09.499 --> 04:11.501
Excuse me while I go upstairs
and sleep,

04:11.626 --> 04:13.419
which I could already be doing
if I didn't take the time

04:13.544 --> 04:14.754
to give my information.

04:15.546 --> 04:18.424
(INDISTINCT CHATTER OVER POLICE RADIO)

04:18.549 --> 04:21.678
Scratch any citizen comes forward
to volunteer information.

04:21.844 --> 04:24.973
You got a 50 percent chance
of uncovering a total asshole.

04:30.687 --> 04:33.481
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)

05:31.331 --> 05:33.333
