05:45.511 --> 05:48.348
Here they were like foxes
waiting at the rabbit hutch.

05:48.556 --> 05:50.767
Made my pickup,
opened the hatch to load it up,

05:51.225 --> 05:53.770
come out to find a damn .38
stuck against my head.

05:54.145 --> 05:56.064
-They took your whole load?
-Just this pickup.

05:56.189 --> 05:57.982
They knew what they was looking for.

05:58.107 --> 05:59.692
I felt like one of those cows

05:59.817 --> 06:01.527
-at the slaughter.
-Three guys?

06:01.778 --> 06:04.030
With masks. One of them named Ramon.

06:04.489 --> 06:06.783
One of the other ones said his name,
and when he did it,

06:06.908 --> 06:09.327
Ramon butt-ended him
in the forehead with his gun.

06:10.828 --> 06:15.416
This gypsy on Mott Street,
she told me in no uncertain terms,

06:15.708 --> 06:16.751
take a change.

06:17.585 --> 06:19.420
Baseline stress just living here.

06:20.671 --> 06:23.674
Hassling with my wife, now this.

06:24.634 --> 06:26.219
I can tell you're upset.

06:26.469 --> 06:31.599
Gypsy said pick a state, starts with "K"
and a town starts with "L."

06:32.600 --> 06:36.479
-I guess Lawrence, Kansas, would fit.
