06:37.188 --> 06:39.107
Churchill Downs Racetrack.

06:40.441 --> 06:41.526
You're leaving now?

06:42.527 --> 06:45.196
-You got a better time in mind?
-You got a truck here.

06:50.660 --> 06:52.078
Hey! Come on.

07:09.178 --> 07:11.222
Yeah, I'm Mike Roberts.
Retired off the job.

07:11.431 --> 07:13.850
-John Irvin, PAA.
-Yeah, I know who you are.

07:14.267 --> 07:15.518
Listen, I was otherwise detained.

07:15.852 --> 07:18.604
I'm the security consultant
for Citiwide Courier.

07:18.688 --> 07:20.690
They had their loaded truck
ripped off this morning.

07:21.149 --> 07:22.859
-Hey, Mike Roberts, Diane.
-Hey.

07:22.984 --> 07:24.152
-How you doin'?
-Okay.

07:24.402 --> 07:25.403
MIKE: Yeah, good.

07:25.695 --> 07:27.822
What, did you catch
that truck hijack this morning?

07:27.905 --> 07:29.240
Mm-hmm. That's us.

07:30.450 --> 07:31.617
-Hi.
-Hi.

07:32.160 --> 07:33.369
Mike Roberts. How's it goin'?

07:34.036 --> 07:36.080
