in a position of your own choice.

07:44.213 --> 07:47.216
Anyways, that's neither here nor there.
Any of the rooms open?

07:47.383 --> 07:48.801
Why, you got something
you want to confess?

07:49.010 --> 07:50.887
It may come to that.
what are you gonna do,

07:51.179 --> 07:53.055
