like a poor relation, or what?

07:53.306 --> 07:55.308
This is about the truck hijacking,
right, Mike?

07:55.391 --> 07:57.643
It's absolutely about the truck hijacking,

07:57.768 --> 07:59.645
regardless of the light
that it puts me in.

08:00.438 --> 08:01.898
