Compound a felony

08:54.367 --> 08:55.868
by concealing my misgivings?

08:56.285 --> 08:57.495
Mistakes happen.

08:58.204 --> 09:01.791
Wait a minute.
When I say compound a felony,

09:02.333 --> 09:04.168
I'm using it as a figure of speech.

09:09.215 --> 09:10.883
Now, how are we gonna say
we got the lead?

09:11.175 --> 09:13.594
