your name into it.

09:13.803 --> 09:15.805
To the perp or Mr. DiNovi.

09:16.514 --> 09:17.557
MIKE: Okay.

09:18.266 --> 09:21.310
-The guy's name is Steve Jung.
-He's Asian?

09:21.727 --> 09:24.397
No. Jung with a "J." He's a Kraut.

09:26.023 --> 09:28.818
His nose chronically buried
in a racing form.

09:29.068 --> 09:31.362
