09:32.029 --> 09:33.698
So, I get a little uneasy feeling.

09:34.031 --> 09:35.908
I sit on him for four hours.

09:36.200 --> 09:38.744
He takes three different meetings
with skells.

09:39.161 --> 09:40.454
One of them I know.

09:40.746 --> 09:43.082
His act's truck hijacks.

09:43.332 --> 09:44.625
Ramon Moreno.

09:44.959 --> 09:47.795
I almost locked him up once, anyways.

09:48.671 --> 09:51.674
-Go do a favor for a friend, right?
-Who's your friend?

09:53.884 --> 09:55.928
Well, this guy's sister,
I know her a little bit.

09:56.012 --> 09:58.097
I met her at some stupid Oktoberfest.

09:58.347 --> 10:00.099
You know, she showed me some leg,

10:00.349 --> 10:02.685
and she said, "My brother Steve's
a ham radio operator.

10:02.810 --> 10:05.187
