by organizing truck hijacks.

10:15.406 --> 10:16.616
(SIGHS)

10:19.493 --> 10:20.995
We'll have to go over this with the boss.

10:21.162 --> 10:25.499
Who no doubt has conveyed to you
that, uh, I'm persona non grata, right?

10:25.875 --> 10:28.377
-Appreciate your help, Mike.
-Yeah.

10:29.712 --> 10:30.921
I'll let myself out.

10:37.094 --> 10:38.679
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

10:41.307 --> 10:44.018
-(TELEPHONE RINGING)
-(SIGHS)

10:44.644 --> 10:45.895
Zippo on canvass.

10:46.896 --> 10:49.357
Mike Roberts just gave us a push
for the inside guy.

10:49.523 --> 10:51.067
A Mike Roberts hire.

10:51.359 --> 10:53.611
JAMES: He runs security
for the truck company, Mike?

10:53.819 --> 10:56.238
-As of the present moment.
-Anything?

10:57.156 --> 10:59.784
We got a push on the dispatcher
for the setup guy.

11:00.326 --> 11:02.078
-Where'd we get that?
-Mike Roberts.

11:02.828 --> 11:05.289
Does this mean we should grab
the dispatcher or rule him out?

11:05.623 --> 11:07.750
We got the delivery
company owner coming in.

11:08.459 --> 11:10.878
-Pick up the dispatcher.
-Yeah.

11:13.297 --> 11:14.548
Did Roberts seem down to you?

11:15.007 --> 11:16.884
(SCOFFS) I'm not real keyed
into his moods.

11:18.177 --> 11:21.222
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

11:23.766 --> 11:26.185
-I'm not going one step further.
-Oh, you're not?

11:26.310 --> 11:28.312
Do I look to you like I'm on Special K?

11:28.479 --> 11:30.356
I'd be passed out
smacking my chin on the floor.

11:30.481 --> 11:33.067
