refers to the illicit substance

11:33.150 --> 11:37.154
on your person,
even if it's not also inside your tummy.

11:37.405 --> 11:39.281
I was holding that deck for someone else.

11:39.365 --> 11:41.992
Does the guy you were holding
it for call you "my friend the moron"?

11:42.118 --> 11:44.620
-Andy.
-Yeah. Roberts, how's it going?

11:44.745 --> 11:46.414
-All right. How you doing?
-Danny Sorenson.

11:46.622 --> 11:48.165
-How's it goin'?
-How's it going? Danny.

11:48.416 --> 11:50.334
Mike Roberts. He's retired off the job.

11:50.543 --> 11:52.378
Joey Fink, holding for a friend.

11:52.670 --> 11:54.755
-Yeah. Novel alibi.
-ANDY: Anyways,

11:55.256 --> 11:56.716
-good to meet you, Mike.
-You too.

11:56.966 --> 11:58.884
Hey, don't budge off that
"holding for a friend."

11:58.968 --> 12:00.261
It's absolutely gonna work for you.

12:01.512 --> 12:05.099
Uh, homicide. This mope's a friend
of the DOA's son.

12:05.474 --> 12:07.560
