on one of the trucks.

12:11.856 --> 12:12.857
Uh-huh.

12:12.940 --> 12:15.776
I was just upstairs. I gave 'em a push
on the hump might have been involved.

12:16.110 --> 12:18.654
-Good.
-Actually, you know what? Hey.

12:19.697 --> 12:22.491
