12:36.589 --> 12:37.631
Please.

12:39.175 --> 12:42.511
-You gonna let go of my hand?
-Yeah. Sorry.

12:44.180 --> 12:47.391
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

13:04.950 --> 13:07.161
