14:46.635 --> 14:49.430
-What's keeping you up nights?
-Other stuff.

14:53.434 --> 14:55.853
Information that I'm privy to. (EXHALES)

14:58.272 --> 14:59.565
Suspicions.

15:01.358 --> 15:02.985
You know, there were times in my life...

15:04.236 --> 15:05.571
when I'd look into the mirror...

15:07.031 --> 15:09.408
and if I was in a situation
like I am right now,

15:09.533 --> 15:10.826
