that I, you know,

17:17.953 --> 17:19.413
keep my eyes away from you.

17:20.622 --> 17:21.623
Did you know that?

17:25.002 --> 17:27.046
Hey, look, I know you got
a case of your own.

17:31.216 --> 17:35.512
Next time you see me, pal...
I'll be on, uh...

17:35.971 --> 17:38.807
Joyce Brothers, uh, call-in help line.

17:39.099 --> 17:44.063
Or that other fruitcake. What's her name?
You know, the, uh, the dwarf, Dr. Ruth.

17:44.813 --> 17:45.856
I'll be with her.

17:51.028 --> 17:52.029
